snippet.title: CoffeeBiz Tycoon Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: CoffeeBiz tycoon is a unique mix of entrepreneurship fun and complicated business simulation. Start your first coffee kiosk, brew, expand, hire, deal with competitors, build a well-known brand, risk, and do everything else needed to build a prosperous and profitable business. Created in isometric pixel art graphic style by a single developer.
